A4.text: Brobee (voiced by Amos Watene) is a little and furry green broccoli bee-like monster. He is around 4 years old as he celebrated his birthday in one episode of the show making him the only one of the Gabba gang to have a confirmed age.

A5.text: Muno (voiced by Adam Deibert) is a red cyclops. He is the tallest member of the Gabba gang. He's so clumsy.
